ontrary to this in Ti/Pt the fluxes of\nrecoils are in counterflow with intermixing Pt atoms and hence slows down the\nnanoscale mass-effect driven ballistic preferential mobility of Pt atoms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 2 Mar 2014 16:47:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-04"}
