ch as Sparse\nApproximated Nearest Points, Mutual Subspace Method and Manifold Discriminant\nAnalysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Mar 2014 06:19:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-27"}
